8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1467858</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/DotDotNews/videos/2301192406624132/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FDotDotNews%2Fvideos%2F2301192406624132%2F&d=cw67THcQ8%2BNa%2BfcBlgGHUxnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=9b7b1e44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/DotDotNews/videos/2301192406624132/</a><br />\n唔好先入為主覺得紅媒抹黑我地，受訪記者係外藉香港人，一直企係示威者呢邊，亦都係撐天琦。被爆眼女手足單野佢都有出片做證。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RichScotford5/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FRichScotford5%2F&d=cw67THcQ8%2BNa%2BfcBlgGHUxnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=2fe49237\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/RichScotford5/</a><br />\n佢出左篇Facebook Post講今晚既感受。<br />\n<br />\n護公安嘅鬼佬記者出咗聲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1467248\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1467248</a>"},{"pid":"5a2eb33be760ea43727414888e51175aa89f2f6a","tid":1468100,"uid":259710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84635b59b5824f4463394e392e180e37b62a7c84","tid":1468100,"uid":217607,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:00:49.000Z","msg":"［轉載］<br />\n<br />\n是咁的<br />\n<br />\n大家好<br />\n我係一條和理非L<br />\n但我絕對支持所有手足<br />\n<br />\n我個人有少少今日嘅反思<br />\n我覺得有一啲基本共識<br />\n喺目前咁多警察嘅情況下<br />\n前線手足都要思考下我哋應唔應該一齊遵守<br />\n<br />\n例如：<br />\n1. 唔可以打記者<br />\n2. 唔可以打救護人員<br />\n3. 唔可以對住除咗警察嘅人使用雷射筆同電筒<br />\n4. 唔可以用私刑<br />\n5. 唔可以攻擊一般平民<br />\n6.如非必要唔好用索帶<br />\n7.唔好阻礙救援同採訪工作<br />\n8.唔好除人衫褲<br />\n9.見到懷疑係鬼嘅人捉住佢之後交記者盤問<br />\n<br />\n大家記唔記得點解我哋攞咗光環啊<br />\n係因為警察做d仆街嘢嘅時候<br />\n我哋冇做<br />\n<br />\n前線無做任何反抗 比十幾隻速龍圍住黎砌 訓低左都要砌 你地會屌<br />\n<br />\n但今日你地就圍住一個比人用索帶綁住嘅fucking man<br />\n<br />\n你地會屌 班狗阻撚住救護車 唔比佢地去救前線 <br />\n<br />\n但你地今日阻住救護人員 唔比佢地救人走<br />\n<br />\n你地會屌班狗當眾抬走一個露晒底嘅女仔走<br />\n<br />\n但你地今日當眾除人褲黎打<br />\n<br />\n有狗對住記者射蛋 你地會屌<br />\n<br />\n但今日有人連立場新聞都打<br />\n<br />\n唔好再嘗試捉鬼喇<br />\n鬼係捉不盡的<br />\n更嚴重嘅係會令到我哋留下心魔<br />\n唔信你身邊嘅手足<br />\n與鬼共舞就係最好嘅方法<br />\n鬼係要煽動大家情緒<br />\n佢混入大家當中<br />\n你估六七月嘅時候冇鬼?<br />\n我哋咪一樣捱咗過嚟<br />\n所以唔使捉鬼<br />\n見到有激動嘅手足勸佢理性冷靜<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唯一嘅解決辦法就係見到身邊手足做不恰當嘅行為嘅時候<br />\n嘗試勸解佢哋<br />\n<br />\n記住<br />\n喺危急嘅時候都要保持冷靜同理性<br />\n<br />\nbtw 絕對唔會同前線割<br />\n我哋而家係做緊賽後檢討<br />\n等呢個運動更加成功<br />\n希望前線手足唔好令天琦失望<br />\n我哋喺磨爛嘅時候<br />\n更加要保持理性同冷靜唔好俾情緒操控我哋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:03:43.000Z","msg":"咁樣小心變成教條主義，限制行動，變成當年嘅金鐘糾察隊，但我認為1，2，5條合理，第5放去第1"},{"pid":"f9ae336024f7d611d8cda434b27b276cbbd67684","tid":1468100,"uid":78554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:03:52.000Z","msg":"14"},{"pid":"f899e648f7e904a9edb87377527c9f3f8123acb2","tid":1468100,"uid":78554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:04:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa77bc36b8faf0b7fb7ab58bd6dce5770a7cfce2","tid":1468100,"uid":78554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:05:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7a3a4214426eb73596a98c2f117f8bb02244390","tid":1468100,"uid":78554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:05:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa3af09801fb5142f846305117506d25caf68c79","tid":1468100,"uid":133728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:06:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2b492ad9927672c9725b00835295d2b7eefb7f94","tid":1468100,"uid":78554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:06:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aff55163bd918f0ee274456b97d2cf0268012c25","tid":1468100,"uid":78554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:07:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0dffb071f41bf79c18fea1632ca94bf45af7651","tid":1468100,"uid":259710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:07:09.000Z","msg":"有時間指責不如趁熱度未退時諗下一步，同溫層外對我地嘅睇法成形後就好難變，唔想再用受傷同血黎換民意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔做都做咗，下一步點？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1467354\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1467354</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\nsorry p牌仔見內容差唔多借位"},{"pid":"156959c0c42793659aff3333c3fc30212572abf6","tid":1468100,"uid":78554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:07:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c4986a4b7866c4ae9acd830d0c7e0697733b66d","tid":1468100,"uid":8584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:08:39.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n我地要檢討 善後 唔係互屌呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n時刻保持冷靜 獨立思考！<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">唔該大家檢討行動唔好用d鬧人既語氣 字眼！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dDEnyS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dDEnyS</a></span>"},{"pid":"ed90bf1df57bd67aeac8c2ed28567f1d82eea9ba","tid":1468100,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:09:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">事實就係今日都係贏<br />\n成個運動拖一日就會多一日比共產黨同港共既壓力<br />\n唔好比支那五毛打擊士氣!!!!!<br />\n港共中共同五毛既目標係消滅抗爭<br />\n佢地做法就係製造內亂打擊士氣<br />\n只要唔好自己放棄就可以玩落去<br />\n多一日贏一日 又成最大贏家了!!!!</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"def25aac281fbe80a4d259633d428da42b69d54e","tid":1468100,"uid":78554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:17:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"962ca42c745e5ef917395aa5ae8d786ff3f6f0dd","tid":1468100,"uid":78554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:17:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e1c5a3534c6e1ca41e6a63d415e99a0bdb76d4a","tid":1468100,"uid":78554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:17:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"486e9ccd56ecbd397d21b6ea2d923b276843e703","tid":1468100,"uid":78554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:18:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7fe27303424619402be7abe20544a9fa742f946","tid":1468100,"uid":78554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:18:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b12b27144c57d4a0962b07d8245a58d4aeebf44f","tid":1468100,"uid":78554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:18:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1497271239740e4c97ce7dff35caf98f99e58675","tid":1468100,"uid":78554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:18:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22bedcc099c722428db8da52665e5272141a8b0c","tid":1468100,"uid":78554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:19:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf1e5c89b434e43caa2fca78eabfbea58a7ce235","tid":1468100,"uid":296350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:19:11.000Z","msg":"不割席 不分化 兄弟爬山<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">弱點已經比敵人對準！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n只要搵幾條仆街帶風就已經成功破解我哋呢三句格言！！<br />\n<br />\n不割不分吖嘛！！<br />\n搵人帶風自然有人跟！！<br />\n搵鬼落場做乜嘢都可以入你數！<br />\n<br />\n再唔諗辦法<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">捉鬼</span></strong>，我哋真係死撚硬！！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">兄弟不割，鬼同分化撚一定要割</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n要有效捉鬼，前線一定要<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">有底線共識</span></strong>，咩可以做，咩唔可以做，一過底線就係鬼，即捉！唔係割席，唔係分化呀！係要<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">認真解決問題呀！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n分化同鬼從來都係狗共致勝之道<br />\n，要對付唯一方法就係<strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">團結</span></strong></strong>！！<br />\n既然團結，就嘗試傾個底線共識，唔係所有野要有共識，底線真係有須要呀！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">一定捉鬼呀！！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">底線共識大家可以討論</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大前提係畀全世界知我哋係<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">為自由良知而戰嘅正義之師，係保護市民嘅黑衣人！！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n1.可以打遊擊同快閃， 唔放火/唔掉磚/唔衝/唔主動出手/唔傷及無無辜。<br />\n<br />\n2. 可以佔路set路障，圍，口撩，還拖！但不主動出擊，不傷及無辜。<br />\n<br />\n3.不送頭，所有可以被聯上暴動同暴徒嘅，都唔好做。<br />\n<br />\n4. 贏輿論同民心唔係講緊連登呀！自high有乜撚嘢用！<br />\n<br />\n輿論係正常媒體包括 social media 同埋國際輿論，民心唔使講啦！<br />\n<br />\n失民心同輿論，話撚知你連登幾high幾高漲，大家可以返屋企含撚啦！<br />\n<br />\n輿論同民心係要嚟令對家喺國際/同社會有壓力！<br />\n<br />\n只要set到個底線嘅共識， <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">我哋先可以真正團結，<strong><strong></strong></strong>先有機會贏</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n咁我先真正做到<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">兄弟爬山 不割席 不分化！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n咁多位手足認真諗諗啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1962b7110a5fc2b8de43a3185b30640a539f2fb","tid":1468100,"uid":8584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:19:20.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n我地要檢討 善後 唔係互屌呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n時刻保持冷靜 獨立思考！<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">唔該大家檢討行動唔好用d鬧人既語氣 字眼！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dDEnyS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dDEnyS</a></span>"},{"pid":"00cd18cd87afb3ea1cd3bf3b542ab605f6eefdc3","tid":1468100,"uid":78554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:19:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dc4fffb13048fa907dfc51a4dace4519e82171a","tid":1468100,"uid":78554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:20:06.000Z","msg":"我個10連<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e1db9e3785c7a10e9071c892750e3bf57364010","tid":1468100,"uid":78554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:20:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ca4af9ea41ca7fbce71968da14d90a98721d497","tid":1468100,"uid":78554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:20:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dd809118cd483011e681333f08f1892e4ee0e60","tid":1468100,"uid":78554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:20:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4b3f0ef1e34409c1d29d840ff9ee806c1aa2d34","tid":1468100,"uid":78554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:21:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a334e6523f88cc8f39e9f3aeb979be268753f697","tid":1468100,"uid":78554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:21:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccf109b11ef14dd2b7c84d39458192710705fc76","tid":1468100,"uid":78554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:21:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1618fbf4a3eaf7b4e7fe794e8768d33be26e7bf2","tid":1468100,"uid":78554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:21:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aad51c356fe8d6e6ac51574ff350183153ed4826","tid":1468100,"uid":78554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:21:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60ba8ba92a2a0979e4969bb287c5833354528e8b","tid":1468100,"uid":168492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:21:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b42c9decc642317124f184501bfa5ab32e3b0da2","tid":1468100,"uid":78554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:21:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7de86041899ef72e7b5da1c296e16120aa0e84df","tid":1468100,"uid":78554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:22:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c9986c1831a246f0b9e6096a09b4375352545e9","tid":1468100,"uid":78554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:23:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85161238eaf3d4a80cfaead6421c3ee5d5445f8f","tid":1468100,"uid":267942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:23:18.000Z","msg":"遇鬼時<br />\n<br />\n1）先捉，<br />\n<br />\n2）圍大圈，分隔 同比多d 記者同人映隻鬼，<br />\n<br />\n個個企到密，根本映唔到。<br />\n<br />\n如鬼或自己人有受傷，都要拍片搵在場醫護幫忙<br />\n<br />\n自己傷固之然要醫護， 亦要係記者前問鬼有冇受傷或身體不適，搵在場醫護幫忙做初步檢查，盡番人道立場同道德高地。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3）搵記者影記錄，重點指出隻鬼做左乜野犯罪行為如打人，煽動，藏有危險品之類，所以採訪101拘捕令。<br />\n<br />\n有物證就映埋物證。同令佢身分曝光，唔好祈望隻鬼會自爆，如果你諗住全世界鏡頭前嚴刑迫供，咁根本係另類送人頭，更何況打死隻鬼，相信佢都唔會講。<br />\n<br />\n闡明你嘅行為係合法性同正當性，同有需要<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4）同時搵議員，叫議員處理/議員報警處理。<br />\n相信10多其9都上白車，popo都放人。<br />\n<br />\n重點係，你留住隻鬼冇乜用，只會令現場仲難控制仲亂，好似今日咁，好易比其他鬼去分化，阻醫護阻記者，<br />\n<br />\n如只做1-4，我知大家可能會好嬲，想發洩，但係隻鬼重點係要佢曝光比世界，囉資料，囉更多頻譜，依個先更有利。<br />\n<br />\n你唔好忘記一舉一動既然係鏡頭前，就要有鏡頭禮儀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n沒有最好的方法，要有改善的辦法"},{"pid":"4c06bdbf67794293e5c14ab5e825fb00171d8027","tid":1468100,"uid":78554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:23:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e15df98e3d7263ef6f659a2012b2d3fa0e5665c0","tid":1468100,"uid":78554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:24:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5da65a9cae981bb0d92a2b65527fb0ec4f151983","tid":1468100,"uid":78554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:24:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2365c64bb1bc78c2d190763deeb7ce500acf4387","tid":1468100,"uid":78554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:24:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05e00a236f891beae1a1adac14ec7cdde188317f","tid":1468100,"uid":78554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:24:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79d3c40fccc9cbd73f7b841fdbe34d6095086cb7","tid":1468100,"uid":78554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:25:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dc9f26a4ebd55a73e861f169825f74404f97b4a","tid":1468100,"uid":78554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:25:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"053c7473af317d12da01df84b4ca60f9f425c1a7","tid":1468100,"uid":78554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-